it.polito.dp2.NFV

Interface VNFTypeReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    NamedEntityReader

    public interface VNFTypeReader
extends NamedEntityReader
    An interface for reading information about a type of VNF, including information about memory and storage required by this type of VNF. The name associated with this interface uniquely identifies the type of VNF within the DP2-NFV system.
